Events.Text: There's a brightly coloured fox sitting by herself here,░ she seems bored,░ her head resting on her palm...░ I don't see anyone else with her, I guess there's no harm in seeing if she wants some company?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Hey there,░ sorry to bother you but you looked a little lonely.░ My name's %playername%, if you wanna talk?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: She jolted in her seat as soon as she heard my voice,░ she was so deep in a daydream I don't think she even noticed me sit down.░ She quickly corrected her posture to something more ladylike.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Oh, I'm really sorry,░ I didn't mean to ignore you...
I've just been having a quiet night and I was kinda tuning out.░ Did you say your name was %playername%?
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text:
Yeah, that's me.░
I know the feeling, I've been having a bit of a quiet night myself.░ Let me guess, did you get dragged here by a friend as well?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: That obvious, huh?░ Yeah, sorta got swept along by people's plans.░ And it was supposed to be my party too..
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text:
So, this was your party?
At a place you don't even like?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Yeah... My school friends insisted they treat me and 'get me out' by taking me to a club.░
Don't get any funny ideas,░ I'm finished with highschool and all,░ they just like to keep in contact every now and then.
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: Are they bad friends or something? Or?...
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
No, it's not that.░ They mean well and all.░ I just don't really have anything in common with them anymore I guess.░ It's not really my thing to go clubbing and get drunk and go hunting for guys and stuff.░
I was only really friends with them because they were in my classes.
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: You couldn't get out of it?░ You must have closer friends right?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I have close friends!░ ...they just live far away.░ I talk to them nearly everyday on the internet.░ One of them did want to come see me for my birthday, but she was busy...
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text:
We meet up every few months at these conventions I go to...░
I'm sorry I'm probably creeping you out with my dorky stuff aren't I?
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text:
You're the one who makes it seem like you're a little out of touch?░
I guess it's good to get out once in a while with friends who are nearby though, right?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Depends on if your local friends just want to booze it up...
I'm sorry,░ I know I'm a bit of a dork.░ How about we change the subject?
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: Yeah let's talk about something else,░ anything in particular you want to ask me?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Now you're putting me on the spot... 
Hmmm?░ N-not really?
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: She seems kind of upset that I talked down her personal life.░ Maybe I should apologize before she loses interest.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Hey I'm sorry for being harsh,░ feel like I was kinda channeling my brother a little there: he's always teasing me about being on my laptop....
You know,░ I'd love to hear more about these cons you go to?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Thanks for being understanding.░
Most people here seem to think I'm weird for all the dorky talk and make an excuse to bail on me.░ I guess it's just because I'm not really looking to jump on a dick if someone so much as flirts with me...
Like I said,░ kinda not really my crowd...
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text:
God, I'm sorry...░
I'm pretty bad at these first impression things aren't I?░ Kinda more thinking what being here says about me than, like... what I should say to people...░
Let's start over.░ My name's Skye by the way!
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: Nice to meet you Skye. Don't worry, I'm not really looking for a fling or anything.░ My junk is firmly locked away, I promise.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Hehehe,░ you're funny %playername%!░ Thanks again for sitting with me,░ who knows how long I'd be sitting around waiting for my friends to finish celebrating on my behalf.░ I sure can pick 'em can't I?░ Hey, can I get you a drink or something?
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: Isn't that something I should be asking you?░ I came over after all.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Oh no.░ Well, I'd appreciate it and everything,░ I'm just not much of a drinker.░ Plus my friends need someone to drive us home.
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: If they aren't going home with someone else of course,░ which they probably will be.
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: Well, okay. Let's both stay sober then,░ only seems fair.░ If you friends bail, we can always grab a drink after to celebrate a little freedom?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
I guess that's true...
Oh, yeah!░ I'm sorry, I kinda go off on tangents a lot.░ You asked about the cons I go to, right?░
First, I guess I wanna ask a test question.░ Do you know why I'm dressed this way at the moment?
Events.Title: Skye

Choices.Text: Your upper body is chilly, but your legs are hot?

Events.Text: Kinda? You're close, try again.
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: Haha!░ No, silly...
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: Nope,░ want me to just tell you?
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: Well, from the conversation, I assume it's something to do with the cons you go to?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Thats right!░ I'm actually a cosplayer,░ this is one of my outfits that looks like one of my favourite characters!░
I've always been a big fan of cartoons,░ comics,░ video game characters and all sorts of stuff.░ Dressing up helps me express myself and a lot of my friends say I do it pretty well too!
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: Ah,░ I think I know the character you're dressing up as!░ You look really cute in that outfit!░ Honestly, you could pass it off as just a normal outfit,░ although a little colourful,░ and...░ well,░ high cut.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Thanks!░
And in the interest of returning the compliment... you look great in that outfit too.
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: How come you're wearing your costume to a club though?░ I don't think you'd find someone else in here that's doing the same thing.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
I know,░ it was a surprise party, my actual birthday was last week and I was experimenting with the fur dye to get the patterns right.░
My mom pretty much opened my door and told me 'Your friends are in the driveway waiting to pick you up!'.░ I wasn't going to go out in my normal clothes while my dye was still fresh!
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: You didn't have time to quickly change?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Well, when I cosplay I dye my fur pretty extensively.░ I didn't want to go through the trouble of trying to explain it to my friends so I just went like this where I could just pretend I was someone else!
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: I think your friends would have known it's you in an outfit.░ They did go to your house afterall, right?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
I know it's kinda dumb,░ but it kinda helps sometimes to be in character, you know?░ Especially if they're a little cooler or more outgoing.░
And,░ hey,░ it's been a good ice breaker with you so far?
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text:
If cosplaying makes you feel more comfortable,░ then I say do it as much as you want.░
I just hopefully you don't feel like you need to hide behind a persona for me,░ you seem like a nice girl when you're being yourself too...
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Thanks %playername%,░ you've been really sweet to listen to me go on and on about myself.░ You seem like a great person and I'd love to get to know more about you.░ But my friends are gonna kill me if we go somewhere else to talk...░ they'll think I went off to sleep with someone.
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: You want me to leave?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
No no! But it's getting late and I was getting ready to leave before you came over.░ I can't really leave my friends hanging after sulking all night and I promised to drive them home soon...
You helped make the night at least a little bit more fun, %playername%, thank you.░ Do you have an IM I can message you at?
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: A what?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Oh, sorry...░ Hold on,░ let me give you my mobile number instead.░ We'll trade instant messengers later!
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Skye takes the receipt for her drink and quickly scribbles a string of numbers on the back, smiling as she hands it over to me.░ I guess she beat me to asking her for it, I must've made a pretty good impression...
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: How about we meet up again soon?░ Somewhere more quiet hopefully!░ That's if you want to of course...░ You don't have to call me!░ We can just talk on Riscord or something, sometime?
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: Thanks,░ Skye,░ I'll let you know when I'm free.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
I'm gonna go find my friends and tell them they can either come home with me now or I'm gonna leave them here...░ this club is making me claustrophobic.░
Thanks again for chatting, %playername%,░ I really enjoyed it!
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: Skye bounced out of her seat,░ taking a quick sip from her drink before slipping over to my side of the booth.░ She gave me a quick hug around my shoulders,░ platonic but grateful,░ as she walked off into the crowd of dancers with her head held a little higher and her tail wagging bushily.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: She seems nice,░ pretty nerdy, which I wasn't expecting from the club.░ I'll call her some time.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Your friends may not have the same interests as you,░ but you deserve a little spoiling for your birthday.░ If they aren't too interested in your costume then that's their loss,░ I'd love to spend a little time admiring your handiwork... 
If I remember rightly,░ that character has some interesting markings that outfit might be hiding.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: That's... You're very flattering, %playername%, but I just can't.░ You seem nice and all,░ and you just want to help me out and everything,░ but I'm not really looking for a quickie tonight.░ If you're looking for someone to fool around with,░ I'm probably not gonna be too good for you right now...
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: There's no better opportunity to explore your deviant side than tonight.░ If you're trying to prove something to your friends, they'll never have to know.░ We can head back to my place,░ and we can do a little roleplay of your favourite character...
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I already told you I'm not like that!░ Hmph! You're no different from anyone else who has tried to 'talk' to me tonight.░ Everyone just wants me to hurry up and get naked for them.░ I have no idea how my friends like this crap.
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: I was just trying to tease you,░ it's not my fault you can't take it.░ It's about give and take here, you know?░ I'm just being  honest about my intentions.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Y'know what?░ I'm just gonna go home.░ I've had enough of this club and its regulars,░ it's making me physically sick.░ Do me a favour and find another girl to flatter with your irresistible charm.

Events.Text: Sorry to be pushy Skye,░ I've had a couple of drinks and it's getting to me.░ I'm not normally like that,░ that's more the club talking than me.░ I'm happy just getting to know you better.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Thats okay, thanks %playername%.░ I'm not dumb,░ I know that's what people normally come to a club for.░ You're not being so out of line to expect as much...░ it just isn't what I'm in the mood for...
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: If you give me a chance to make it up to you,░ I will.░ Honestly, I've been enjoying our chat most of all this evening.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
I think I might head home actually,░ I've had a pretty bad night.░
You seem like a nice enough person, %playername%,░ I can't believe you've listened to me going on about having a shitty time for so long.░
I owe you for making my night at least a little better at the end.░ Do you have an IM I can message you at?
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: A what?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Oh, sorry...░ Hold on,░ let me give you my mobile number instead.░ We'll trade instant messengers later.
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: Skye takes the receipt for her drink and quickly scribbles a string of numbers on the back, smiling as she hands it over to me.░ I guess she beat me to asking her for it, I must've made a pretty good impression...
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Buzz me sometime and I might answer,░ who knows!

Events.Text: Skye gathered her belongings,░ giving me a grateful wink that seemed a little overconfident as she headed into the crowd of dancers with her arms folded across her chest.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: She seems nice,░ pretty nerdy, which I wasn't expecting from the club.░ I'll call her some time.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: I'm sorry but this is getting kinda deep for me,░ you seem nice but I think I might go see who else is here tonight.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: What really?░ I creeped you out that much?
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text:
Well I can't change your mind, I guess.░
Thanks for talking to me for a little while %playername%, you seem kinda nice.░ I might just find my friends and go home a little early. 
Maybe I'll see you around though?
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: Skye gathered her belongings,░ taking a quick sip from her water before scribbling her number down and leaving the glass pinning it down for me to take rather than handing it me.░ She walked slowly off into the crowd of dancers with her arms folded across her chest, looking a little embarrassed.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: It's best I leave her alone for now,░ if I want to talk to her again I'll call her later.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Thats really unfortunate to hear.░ Needing to get into a costume to go out isn't exactly healthy, right?
To be honest now that I know you aren't even in your natural fur colour,░ that's a little extreme...
Just saying,░ should you be... I dunno, <i>concerned?

Events.Text:
Normal girls don't do that kind of stuff,░ these con 'friends' you say you have sound kinda like dorks that have nothing better to do with their lives than get you to play pretend...░
Your true friends are out there having the time of their lives on that dance floor...░ You should be out there having fun with them rather than cooped up in a booth sulking on your phone.

Events.Text: I'm sorry for being different okay?!░ You make it sound like I need, what? Counseling?░ I can't believe you'd say something cruel like that to me...░ How would you like it if I told you everything you like is stupid and has no meaning?
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: I was just being honest.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Y'know what?░ I'm just gonna go home.░ I've had enough of this club and its regulars,░ it's making me physically sick.░ Do me a favor and find another girl to tell how they should be living their life...

Events.Text: Skye snatched up her things and rammed them into her pockets.░ She got to her feet in a huff and stormed off into the crowd of dancers.

Events.Text: I guess I should leave her alone for now...

Events.Text: I have no clue,░ care to tell?

Events.Text:
I'm actually a cosplayer,░ someone who dresses up as a famous character,░ this is one of my outfits that looks like one of my favourite characters!░
I've always been a big fan of cartoons,░ comics,░ video game characters and all sorts of stuff.░ Dressing up helps me express myself and a lot of my friends say I do it pretty well too!

Events.Text: Nice to meet you Skye.░ Don't worry,░ I'll resist dragging you off for now. We can both keep guard!

Events.Text: Nice to meet you Skye.░ No wonder you scare off all the guys,░ you're sooner to talk about their cock then you are telling them your name!

Events.Text: I'll think about it,░ for now I think I'll go look around the club some more.░ See you later?

What do you all do when you go to those conventions anyway?

Events.Text: As I took a perch on the edge of the booth I made a fake cough, followed by an exaggerated 'Ahem'.░ The fox girl jolted in her seat,░ she was so deep in a daydream I don't think she'd even noticed me sit down.░ She quickly corrected her posture to something more ladylike.

I didn't mean to ignore you, ░I've just been having a quiet night and was kinda tuning out.░
What's your name?

Events.Text: %playername%. I've been having a bit of a quiet night too, so I know the feeling.░ Let me guess, did you get dragged here by a friend as well?

Events.Text: I give the nearest leg of the table a firm bash with the heel of my foot,░ causing a loud thud,░ she almost jumped completely off her seat in surprise.░ Her glass of water almost teetering over before calming.░ She began exhaling heavily,░ her hand clenching her chest.

Events.Text: Holy shit,░ That scared the hell out of me!░ You almost gave me a heart attack.

Events.Text: Why did you go and do that anyway?!░ Who even does that to someone?░ You have a really dumb way of getting someone's attention!

Ah, shit... 
Look,░ I'm sorry,░ I thought it was funny but it wasn't.░ I'm kinda nervous here and was trying to make a big entrance... it was stupid...
Can we try starting over?░ My name's %playername% if you'd like someone to chat with?

It's ok,░ I guess I overreacted a little as well.░

Events.Text: <i>I should probably leave her alone.

I'm sorry, words couldn't express how cute you are,░ so I let my saliva do the talking.

Come on, it's a compliment.

Events.Text:
I know, right? That's what I was thinking!░
Well that and I can't just go around in my bare fur.
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text:
Hah... if there was a place for it, this would be it.░
Did you know they have a pool upstairs?
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>She blushed deeply and hid her snout behind her soda.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
I'm totally not going nude around a pool just to show off the markings...░
Anyway, the purple dye goes all green and weird...
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text:
W-what?░
Oh, no!░ I meant, like, a swimsuit or something...
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
<i>Though, again,░ if there was a place for clothing-optional showing off, I guess it was Amorous' pool...
Damn,░ now that's an image I'd be hapy to take out of here...
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Oh... Yeah right.░
Duh... I knew that...░
And in the interest of returning the compliment... you look great in that outfit too, by the way!
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: I dunno if I'd have the nerve to try and pull off a cosplay that complicated with the dye, so kudos!
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
So much for 'I'm a nerd too Skye'...░
Thanks for being a jerk...
Events.Title: Skye

Events.Text: We'll have to talk more shop about anime and gaming too!░ Now I know there's someone local who's into that stuff!
Events.Title: Skye
